<body>

    <!-- Main Content for How to Use Section -->
    <div id="how-to-use" style="max-width: 1200px; margin: 20px auto; padding: 20px; background-color: #fff; border-radius: 12px; box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);">
        <h1 style="text-align: center; font-size: 36px; color: #3498db; margin-bottom: 20px;">How to Use Our Recharge Platform</h1>

        <!-- Step 1 -->
        <div class="step" style="margin-bottom: 30px;">
            <h2 style="font-size: 24px; color: #333;">Step 1: Sign In or Register</h2>
            <p style="font-size: 18px; color: #555; line-height: 1.6;">If you already have an account, simply <a href="login.jsp">log in</a> using your credentials. If you are a new user, <a href="register.jsp">sign up</a> to create a new account.</p>
        </div>

        <!-- Step 2 -->
        <div class="step" style="margin-bottom: 30px;">
            <h2 style="font-size: 24px; color: #333;">Step 2: Enter Your Mobile Number</h2>
            <p style="font-size: 18px; color: #555; line-height: 1.6;">Once logged in, enter the mobile number you wish to recharge in the provided field. Make sure you enter a valid number and select the correct operator from the dropdown.</p>
        </div>

        <!-- Step 3 -->
        <div class="step" style="margin-bottom: 30px;">
            <h2 style="font-size: 24px; color: #333;">Step 3: Choose a Plan</h2>
            <p style="font-size: 18px; color: #555; line-height: 1.6;">Browse through the list of available plans and offers for your operator. Select the one that suits your needs the best.</p>
        </div>

        <!-- Step 4 -->
        <div class="step" style="margin-bottom: 30px;">
            <h2 style="font-size: 24px; color: #333;">Step 4: Make Payment</h2>
            <p style="font-size: 18px; color: #555; line-height: 1.6;">Proceed to the payment page. You can pay using various payment methods like credit/debit cards, net banking, UPI, or e-wallets. All transactions are secure and encrypted.</p>
        </div>

        <!-- Step 5 -->
        <div class="step" style="margin-bottom: 30px;">
            <h2 style="font-size: 24px; color: #333;">Step 5: Confirmation</h2>
            <p style="font-size: 18px; color: #555; line-height: 1.6;">After a successful payment, you will receive a confirmation message with details of your recharge. You will also receive an email confirmation for your records.</p>
        </div>

        <!-- Additional Help Section -->
        <div class="step" style="margin-bottom: 30px;">
            <h2 style="font-size: 24px; color: #333;">Need Help?</h2>
            <p style="font-size: 18px; color: #555; line-height: 1.6;">If you face any issues during the recharge process, feel free to <a href="contacts.jsp">contact us</a> for support.</p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Footer -->
    <footer style="text-align: center; padding: 20px; background-color: #3498db; color: #fff; margin-top: 40px; border-radius: 12px;">
